QuestData.Title: Return to the Spirit Talker
QuestData.Description: You have done what was asked, and now I give you that which you desire.$B$BDeliver this primal to the spirit talker back at your Bor'gorok Outpost. If she is wise, she will know a ritual to gain you the information which you seek.
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver Imperean's Primal to Spirit Talker Snarlfang at Bor'gorok Outpost.
QuestData.CompletionText: $n, you have returned. What did you learn?$B$BWhat is that sound?
QuestData.RewardText: Imperean gave you a primal essence of herself? I can hear its howling winds!$B$BI know a ritual we can make use of it in. We must hurry before her primal rips itself apart!
